node.text:
✨Introducing our new IGTV series, Dunkin’ DIY! ✨.
🍩Every week, we’ll be sharing an awesome Dunkin’-themed DIY project with you.
☕️Whether it’s recipes from our culinary team, Dunkin’-themed home projects, and everything in between, these creations are on 🔥
🍪Our first episode features Angie, @sweetlyicedbakery, decorating Dunkin’ cookies.🍪🎥Check out the full video on IGTV. You can also grab the recipe on our blog: news.dunkindonuts.com/blog.
.
Have a Dunkin’ DIY you want to share with us? Let us know in the comments below! ⬇️
